# validate wiring rule

`signalos validate` mirrors the severity tiers of deliver.sh validators.

- A HALT failure (exit 1) must be resolved before any merge.
- A BLOCK_MERGE failure (exit 2) must be resolved before closing a wave.
- WARN failures (exit 0) are advisory; log but do not block.
- Use `--validator <name>` to target a specific guard for faster CI loops.
